  • Constructor Details

    • MenuSubScene

      public MenuSubScene()
      Creates a widget styled scene for menu sub scene. The scene is layout according to the screen. a background image is also set which is bluePanel.

  • Method Details

    • moveSubScene

      public void moveSubScene()
      Transition effect while a menu sub scene is closed and opened. Plays accordingly when it's hidden or visible.
